Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Prologue}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:22.00,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:52.05,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:07.00,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.08,0:22:30.08,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:00.04,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Epilogue}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.94,0:00:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There! Look!{Kiyomizudera, nice.}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.35,0:00:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just there! Kyoto Station!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.73,0:00:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, seriously?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.96,0:02:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, no way.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.27,0:02:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nino?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.93,0:02:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one else here, is there?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.44,0:02:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What? This is my room.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.05,0:02:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you care?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.19,0:02:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think is paying for it?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.94,0:03:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't have to be such a fancy private room.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.37,0:03:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The nurses are gossiping about how I might be the hospital director's bastard son.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.16,0:03:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you expect?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.92,0:03:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The girls thought you were going to die.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.16,0:03:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father was the one who paid for my hospital expenses too, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.21,0:03:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.36,0:03:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Which basically means {\i1}we{\i0} paid for them.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.27,0:03:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought you of all people would come visit me, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.24,0:03:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.21,0:03:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot, I have to get going!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.61,0:03:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare tell anyone about this, all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.86,0:03:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-san}, was Nino just here?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.55,0:03:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yotsuba?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.27,0:03:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.64,0:03:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't seen you since the school trip.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.35,0:03:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.52,0:03:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And the rest of you...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.32,0:03:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.54,0:03:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're alive, at least.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.24,0:04:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.71,0:04:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Who ever asked you to come?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.65,0:04:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely smell Nino.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.76,0:04:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sniff, sniff...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.90,0:04:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she smell {\i1}that{\i0} bad?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.90,0:04:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor girl...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.59,0:04:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We weren't sure you were going to make it, at one point.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.88,0:04:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your temperature was as high as a record-breaking summer day.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.44,0:04:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're feeling better.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.43,0:04:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You can call if you ever get lonely.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.48,0:04:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll come take care of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.75,0:04:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.80,0:04:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I prefer being by myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.25,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.34,0:04:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong answer, Futaro{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.31,0:04:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, here.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.48,0:04:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Handouts from class while you were sick.{That's a lot of freaking printouts.}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.37,0:04:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing I finally got them to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.84,0:04:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're going to school, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.92,0:04:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.65,0:04:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I might quit school.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.63,0:05:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You were never that committed, were you?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.11,0:05:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you're so mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there something you didn't like?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.89,0:05:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.23,0:05:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've cooked for you if you'd asked me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.36,0:05:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just don't really have an appetite. {brah it's fucking obvious her cooking tastes like ass}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.72,0:05:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Say "ahh".
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.34,0:05:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.40,0:05:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better eat.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.60,0:05:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.04,0:05:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.42,0:05:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I found Nino!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.18,0:06:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What are you, a dog?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.67,0:06:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.31,0:06:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}L-Let me go!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.03,0:06:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'd better be going.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.04,0:06:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you get better soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.80,0:06:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.12,0:06:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.92,0:06:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel a little better.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.49,0:06:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being discharged tomorrow, aren't you, Uesugi{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.55,0:06:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.02,0:06:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you worried about your studies?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.69,0:06:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.24,0:06:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing fine,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.24,0:06:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but there are some idiots that I have to teach.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.61,0:06:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.61,0:06:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That concludes your examination.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.32,0:06:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop shoving!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.96,0:06:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence in the hospital, Nino.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.20,0:06:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.59,0:06:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was scared!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.93,0:06:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Those girls...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.68,0:06:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I should thank them for coming to visit.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.47,0:07:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're never going to get your ears pierced if you're afraid of needles.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.71,0:07:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Needles?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.33,0:07:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.68,0:07:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you guys actually here for?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.76,0:07:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.45,0:07:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Vaccinations.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.44,0:07:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We always get vaccinated around this time every year.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.21,0:07:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But Itsuki and Nino keep running away.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.07,0:07:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate pain.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.88,0:07:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we got to see Uesugi{**-san} while we were at it, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.89,0:07:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You what...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.38,0:07:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you all! You're going to get it!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.01,0:07:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.81,0:07:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No shouting in the hospital!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.47,0:07:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sick! Rest up!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.11,0:07:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-kun}...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.17,0:07:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect great things from you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.49,0:08:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Uesugi Futaro{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.46,0:08:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I remember that?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.89,0:08:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just you, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.87,0:08:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.84,0:08:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I could say the same to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.79,0:08:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yotsuba and the others have been looking for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.70,0:08:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.93,0:08:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to ask you a question.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.25,0:08:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, why do you study?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.02,0:08:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's my job as a student.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.69,0:08:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.39,0:08:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.03,0:08:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to keep staring at you until you tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.21,0:08:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.60,0:09:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to keep staring at you until you give up?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.32,0:09:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.86,0:09:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see who surrenders first.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.60,0:09:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, young love.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.17,0:09:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.15,0:09:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not leaving until you tell me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.04,0:09:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.47,0:09:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I win!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.93,0:09:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you're getting the dare.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.37,0:09:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please, anything but {\i1}that{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.84,0:09:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been able to eat fish since last time!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Futaro!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.92,0:09:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the train. Be quiet.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.26,0:09:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Takebayashi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.79,0:09:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on a school trip!\N Stop being a goody-two-shoes and join us!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.13,0:09:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, fine, I will.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.45,0:09:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You should invite Sanada{**-kun} too, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.17,0:09:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the five of us in this group.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.06,0:09:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.33,0:09:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Arithmetic drills?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.72,0:10:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you, stupid?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.28,0:10:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw out all that useless junk!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.49,0:10:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, this is the only thing that matters.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.62,0:10:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's awesome.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.47,0:10:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so cool.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.16,0:10:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I swiped it from my dad's work stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.11,0:10:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Takebayashi?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.72,0:10:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to take...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.38,0:10:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.91,0:10:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two have known each other since they were little.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.14,0:10:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They live nearby, and their parents are close, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.39,0:10:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Their families have even gone on trips together.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.12,0:10:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're both class reps.\N They look good together, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.03,0:10:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Futaro. Stop taking pictures.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.60,0:10:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.66,0:10:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.42,0:10:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.97,0:10:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My stomach suddenly started hurting.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.12,0:10:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn gut... Got me good.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.44,0:10:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to hit the bathroom.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.86,0:10:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch up later.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.79,0:10:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw out all that useless junk!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.60,0:11:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.43,0:11:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.97,0:11:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You took a picture of me just now, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.96,0:11:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you want, lady?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You snuck a photo of me!{QC - Bah I always struggle when this comes up. Second opinion? prev: "sneak photo"}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.19,0:11:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He snuck a photo of me!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I never did!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.51,0:11:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.08,0:11:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This kid fell for my beauty! He snuck pictures of me!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrest him! Arrest him!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.18,0:11:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Did not!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.39,0:11:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there, calm down.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.63,0:11:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check his camera, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.31,0:11:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, would you mind showing it to me?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.34,0:11:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.49,0:11:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.45,0:11:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I... um...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.36,0:11:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's innocent.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.85,0:11:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw what happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.88,0:12:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how my school trip ended.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What was {\i1}that{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.35,0:12:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the part I wanted to hear about! And you ended it so abruptly!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.93,0:12:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens to Earth?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.06,0:12:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I never said I'd tell you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.71,0:12:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.00,0:12:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The only reason I did what you asked
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.00,0:12:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,was to thank you for coming the other day.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.62,0:12:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't sound that grateful.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.51,0:12:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can see that you've changed a great deal since then.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.01,0:12:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Meeting that girl changed you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.07,0:13:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, lucky charms!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's buy some!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.53,0:13:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you following me?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.14,0:13:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.47,0:13:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I can change too?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.10,0:13:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to help me change, if you could.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.16,0:13:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking for someone, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.19,0:13:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I am too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.36,0:13:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can find them myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.28,0:13:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ask someone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be anyone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.56,0:13:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We're both alone and lonely.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.07,0:13:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to stick together.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.17,0:13:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I need...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.15,0:13:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We need you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.42,0:13:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.26,0:13:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's take a picture together.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.42,0:13:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, I never said you could touch it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.69,0:13:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.53,0:13:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any use in having me teach you?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.26,0:13:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Your average test score is a 29.6. {fr? these grils should quit school and become models lmao}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.44,0:13:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make it work.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.99,0:14:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do everything we can.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.00,0:14:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.20,0:14:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I dug up my old lucky charm.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.32,0:14:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're resorting to prayer?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.08,0:14:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, where did you buy those?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.67,0:14:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,These?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.42,0:14:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember if I bought them or if someone gave them to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.83,0:14:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they're from Kyoto, five years ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.09,0:14:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Itsuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.72,0:14:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.22,0:14:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We were looking all over for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.97,0:14:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, now that the five of us are here.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.86,0:14:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Itsuki, I'm going to do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.64,0:14:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're going down with me!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.97,0:14:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.35,0:15:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}just{\i0} got out of the hospital. What do you want?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.36,0:15:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.69,0:15:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you want us all to wear our hair the same way?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.00,0:15:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Itsuki! Miku! Yotsuba! Nino! Ichika!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.84,0:15:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nino! Miku! Itsuki! Yotsuba! Ichika!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.24,0:15:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't tutoring us today?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.99,0:15:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You seem pretty enthusiastic, Nino.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.24,0:15:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} Nino.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So there you have it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.55,0:15:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Without any hints, I don't know who's who.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.04,0:15:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like one of those recent idol groups!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.02,0:15:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's just because you're disinterested.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.10,0:15:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.45,0:16:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for having me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.88,0:16:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.47,0:16:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.07,0:16:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But I pushed the doorbell!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.23,0:16:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is this...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.35,0:16:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A zero in every subject.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.83,0:16:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And she went to the trouble of tearing her name off every sheet.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.33,0:16:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell who it was because she was in a bath towel,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.60,0:16:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but the culprit is among us.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.77,0:16:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yotsuba, fess up. {get em, kirito, goddamn! what is this savagery?}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.28,0:16:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just going to assume it was me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.59,0:16:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why you had us all do our hair the same way.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.31,0:16:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you tell each other apart just by your faces?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.39,0:16:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.23,0:16:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.22,0:16:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who else but Miku has such a bland face?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.67,0:16:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No one else but Nino has such an annoying face.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.23,0:16:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "bland"?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.68,0:16:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And what do you mean by "annoying"?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.30,0:16:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}By "annoying", I mean annoying.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.87,0:16:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-san}, let me tell you something useful.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.76,0:16:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're bland because you're bland!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.05,0:16:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mother taught us how to tell each other apart a long time ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.59,0:17:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Love will show you the way!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.00,0:17:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder I couldn't tell.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.29,0:17:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we let our hair down now?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.89,0:17:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so serious today?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.49,0:17:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I smell shampoo...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.97,0:17:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kind of creepy.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.56,0:17:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.05,0:17:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to do something for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.04,0:17:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me a pervert.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.90,0:17:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a hopeless pervert.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.72,0:17:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it. It didn't sound so hurtful.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.95,0:17:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell us apart by our moles.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.29,0:17:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.90,0:17:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.91,0:17:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.45,0:17:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.65,0:17:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind showing you, Futaro.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.80,0:17:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.05,0:17:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to help if you haven't seen the culprit's mole, is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.74,0:17:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.44,0:18:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Futaro{**-kun}, it could be that the culprit isn't among us.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.16,0:18:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.02,0:18:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be shocked, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.85,0:18:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We are sextuplets and have a secret sixth sister, Mutsumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.65,0:18:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.19,0:18:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where is Mutsumi right now?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.33,0:18:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in a secret room, unknown to any of us.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.73,0:18:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Forget this.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.56,0:18:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't getting anywhere. Whatever.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.37,0:18:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for the last resort!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.47,0:18:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to do this?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.81,0:18:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is outrageous.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.06,0:18:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Futaro's kind of pushy today.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.86,0:19:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.67,0:19:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done first.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.47,0:19:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the culprit.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.77,0:19:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.62,0:19:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.46,0:19:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I even changed my handwriting!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.45,0:19:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.71,0:19:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you write the letter "b".
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.44,0:19:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered you were the only one who writes it cursive.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.43,0:20:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know you well enough to tell apart your faces,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.91,0:20:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've seen your handwriting more often than I'd like.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.37,0:20:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.39,0:20:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You got me!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.15,0:20:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.71,0:20:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of us finished, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.15,0:20:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. Let me grade you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.90,0:20:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Itsuki's "so" is the same as the culprit.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.16,0:20:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And Nino's "mon" radical...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.08,0:20:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Miku's "four".
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.69,0:20:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yotsuba's kanji suffix.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.44,0:20:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all the same as the culprit's!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.64,0:20:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one of you failed a quiz!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.69,0:20:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Busted.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.93,0:20:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done, Ichika?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.16,0:20:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You were supposed to hide them before he got here!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.80,0:20:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.93,0:20:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stuck in hospital for a while,\N and this is what happens?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.04,0:20:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you're all...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.67,0:20:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.91,0:21:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason you were trying so hard to tell us apart...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.56,0:21:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It has something to do with that girl from five years ago you mentioned, right? {itsuki sure isn't stupid lmao}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.53,0:21:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it's one of us, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.28,0:21:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.28,0:21:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point in buying all of those?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.89,0:21:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is to make me try five times harder.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.38,0:21:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to become an example for the others.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.01,0:21:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise your hand if you met me a long time ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.36,0:21:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd that come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.29,0:21:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.44,0:21:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Figures.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.65,0:21:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that girl was one of you idiots.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.26,0:21:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How dare you call us idiots?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.84,0:21:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not wrong, am I?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.64,0:21:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you've been hiding the exams you bombed.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.64,0:21:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're spending all day today on review.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.04,0:21:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Itsuki...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.86,0:22:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that on purpose?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.61,0:22:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about you anymore, Futaro.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.60,0:22:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.84,0:22:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you need to do some studying first, Uesugi{**-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.92,0:24:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Seven Goodbyes, Part 1."
Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.25,0:00:04.24,Italics,,0,0,0,,I was dreaming...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.44,0:00:20.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,Dreaming about the day we first met.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.81,0:02:13.82,Italics,,0,0,0,,Our school trip was one disaster after another.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.82,0:02:16.44,Italics,,0,0,0,,And then my mild cold turned into a full-blown flu.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.89,0:02:21.37,Italics,,0,0,0,,It all ended with me going straight to the hospital.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.47,0:02:28.73,Italics,,0,0,0,,And I get the feeling...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.32,0:02:33.72,Italics,,0,0,0,,they came to pay me a visit.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.36,0:03:25.72,Italics,,0,0,0,,Yikes. I didn't think anyone could be such a brat.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.64,0:04:15.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's my perfume!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.83,0:05:08.47,Italics,,0,0,0,,I thought school was boring...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.47,0:05:10.86,Italics,,0,0,0,,That I wouldn't have any problems quitting.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.52,0:05:13.62,Italics,,0,0,0,,But I'm going to stay a little longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.56,0:05:17.12,Italics,,0,0,0,,There's something I can't leave behind now.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.95,0:05:21.29,Italics,,0,0,0,,You're aloof, insensitive, and mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.41,0:05:23.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,So why...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.53,0:05:28.44,Italics,,0,0,0,,does it have to be you?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.76,0:07:47.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've seen that man somewhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.25,0:07:53.12,Italics,,0,0,0,,It was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.11,0:07:59.98,Italics,,0,0,0,,But it's a scene that's etched firmly in my mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.44,0:08:04.49,Italics,,0,0,0,,Right, that was...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.37,0:12:09.47,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is an emergency!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.47,0:12:12.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\an8}An unidentified flying object has emerged over Japan!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.21,0:12:15.47,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We come from the planet of Shogi.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.47,0:12:19.51,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The most capable player in Japan shall play me for the fate of planet Earth.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.85,0:14:15.26,Italics,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, that girl bought similar ones, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.88,0:14:16.95,Italics,,0,0,0,,A ton of them.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.63,0:14:18.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,Five of them.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.39,0:14:58.58,Italics,,0,0,0,,Five years ago...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.30,0:15:00.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,In Kyoto...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.83,0:15:05.97,Italics,,0,0,0,,It has to be a coincidence, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.15,0:15:55.37,Italics,,0,0,0,,This happened just ten minutes ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.51,0:18:35.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,This problem set has questions from the earlier exams.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.16,0:18:39.47,Italics,,0,0,0,,The one who does the worst is the culprit.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.45,0:18:55.07,Italics,,0,0,0,,You're stuck now, Futaro{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.67,0:19:00.29,Italics,,0,0,0,,I panicked and kicked you out in a hurry,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.29,0:19:02.82,Italics,,0,0,0,,but that seems to have worked to my advantage.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.34,0:19:08.41,Italics,,0,0,0,,I'd let my guard down on the quiz,\N but I can do well if I try.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.11,0:19:12.58,Italics,,0,0,0,,Sorry everyone, let's get this over with.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.96,0:19:15.84,Italics,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.24,0:19:17.59,Italics,,0,0,0,,My handwriting!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.33,0:19:22.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,He's casually going to compare our handwriting.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.20,0:19:24.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,Not bad, Futaro{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.60,0:19:26.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,Close call.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.16,0:19:30.54,Italics,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who can dry my hair so quickly.
