Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.53,0:22:19.29,Italics,,0,0,0,,quintuplets can be quite different.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.97,0:22:22.39,Italics,,0,0,0,,Still, for now,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.39,0:22:27.77,Italics,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'm going to be able to tell them apart without their handwriting.

